  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CombatBox is a war simulation game where AI factions fight each other.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features:</strong></u></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AI Battles</strong>: Engage in battles where soldiers fight for survival. Strategy is key to gaining the upper hand.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/71dfcb72871fd2d7a12dec01ac063c33.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Limb Dismemberment & Blood System</strong>: Experience the harshness of war with realistic limb dismemberment and blood effects that heighten the intensity of battle.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/aab79583ad29a181580897cabc75f035.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics-Driven Bullets</strong>: Bullets follow realistic trajectories, providing a challenging and immersive combat experience.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/623b87494debd2efeea85b173224f632.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Weaponry</strong>: Equip yourself with a wide array of weapons, each suited for different tactics and combat scenarios.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/7134db81972f1fd03d4f076bef914929.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upcoming Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mod Support</strong>: Expand the game with custom content, allowing players to create and share new scenarios and experiences.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CombatBox is a war simulation game where AI factions fight each other.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features:</strong></u></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AI Battles</strong>: Engage in battles where soldiers fight for survival. Strategy is key to gaining the upper hand.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/71dfcb72871fd2d7a12dec01ac063c33.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Limb Dismemberment & Blood System</strong>: Experience the harshness of war with realistic limb dismemberment and blood effects that heighten the intensity of battle.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/aab79583ad29a181580897cabc75f035.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics-Driven Bullets</strong>: Bullets follow realistic trajectories, providing a challenging and immersive combat experience.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/623b87494debd2efeea85b173224f632.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Weaponry</strong>: Equip yourself with a wide array of weapons, each suited for different tactics and combat scenarios.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3591890/extras/7134db81972f1fd03d4f076bef914929.avif?t=1768413917\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upcoming Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mod Support</strong>: Expand the game with custom content, allowing players to create and share new scenarios and experiences.</p></li></ul>",
